  </span>
 </p>
 <p>
  <strong>Integral</strong>
 </p>
 <p>
  Value -
  <span class="eq">
   <var>I</var>
   <sub>B</sub>
   =
   <span class="dvc">
    2 ·
    <var>h</var>
    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    45
   </span>
   ·  ( 2 · 7 ·
   <var>y</var>
   <sub>1</sub>
   + 2 · 32 ·
   <var>y</var>
   <sub>2</sub>
   + 12 ·
   <var>y</var>
   <sub>3</sub>
   )  =
   <span class="dvc">
    2 · 0.5
    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    45
   </span>
   ·  ( 2 · 7 · 0 + 2 · 32 · 0.866 + 12 · 1 )  = 1.5
  </span>
 </p>
 <p>
  Error -
  <span class="eq">
   <var>δ</var>
   <sub>B</sub>
   =
   <span class="dvc">
    <b class="b0">|</b>
