 <h4>Tanh-sinh rule</h4>
 <hr/>
 <p>
  Boundary of the interval -
  <span class="eq">
   <var>t</var>
   <sub>a</sub>
   = 1
  </span>
 </p>
 <p>
  Step -
  <span class="eq">
   <var>h</var>
   =
   <span class="dvc">
    2 ·
    <var>t</var>
    <sub>a</sub>
    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    <var>n</var>
    − 1
   </span>
   =
   <span class="dvc">
    2 · 1
    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    5 − 1
   </span>
   = 0.5
  </span>
 </p>
 <p>
  Parameters -
  <span class="eq">
   <var>t</var>
   (
   <var>k</var>
   )  = -
   <var>t</var>
   <sub>a</sub>
   +  (
   <var>k</var>
   − 1 )  ·
   <var>h</var>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p>
  Function for abscissas -
  <span class="eq">
   <var>x</var>
   (
   <var>k</var>
   )  =
   <b>tanh</b>
   <span class="b1">(</span>
   <span class="dvc">
    <var>π</var>
    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    2
   </span>
   ·
   <b>sinh</b>
   (
   <var>t</var>
   (
   <var>k</var>
   )  )
   <span class="b1">)</span>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p>
  Weight function -
  <span class="eq">
   <var>w</var>
   (
   <var>k</var>
   )  =
   <span class="dvc down">
    <var>π</var>
    ·
    <var>h</var>
    ·
    <b>cosh</b>
    (
    <var>t</var>
    (
    <var>k</var>
    )  )
    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    2 ·
    <b>cosh</b>
    <span class="b1">(</span>
    <span class="dvc">
     <var>π</var>
     <span class="dvl">
     </span>
     2
    </span>
    ·
    <b>sinh</b>
    (
    <var>t</var>
    (
    <var>k</var>
    )  )
    <span class="b1">)</span>
    <sup class="raised">2</sup>
   </span>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p>
  <strong>Abscissas,       Ordinates,         Weights</strong>
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>x</var>
   <sub>1</sub>
   =
   <var>x</var>
   ( 1 )  = -0.951
  </span>
  ,
  <span class="eq">
   <var>y</var>
   <sub>1</sub>
   =
   <var>f</var>
   (
   <var>x</var>
   <sub>1</sub>
   )  =
   <var>f</var>
   ( -0.951 )  = 0.308
  </span>
  ,
  <span class="eq">
   <var>w</var>
   <sub>1</sub>
   =
   <var>w</var>
   ( 1 )  = 0.115
  </span>
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>x</var>
   <sub>2</sub>
   =
   <var>x</var>
   ( 2 )  = -0.674
  </span>
  ,
  <span class="eq">
   <var>y</var>
   <sub>2</sub>
   =
   <var>f</var>
   (
   <var>x</var>
   <sub>2</sub>
   )  =
   <var>f</var>
   ( -0.674 )  = 0.738
  </span>
  ,
  <span class="eq">
   <var>w</var>
   <sub>2</sub>
   =
   <var>w</var>
   ( 2 )  = 0.483
  </span>
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>x</var>
   <sub>3</sub>
   =
   <var>x</var>
   ( 3 )  = 0
  </span>
  ,
  <span class="eq">
   <var>y</var>
   <sub>3</sub>
   =
   <var>f</var>
   (
   <var>x</var>
   <sub>3</sub>
   )  =
   <var>f</var>
   ( 0 )  = 1
  </span>
  ,
  <span class="eq">
   <var>w</var>
   <sub>3</sub>
   =
   <var>w</var>
   ( 3 )  = 0.785
  </span>
 </p>
 <p>
  <strong>Integral</strong>
 </p>
 <p>
  Value -
  <span class="eq">
   <var>I</var>
   <sub>DE</sub>
   = 2 ·
   <var>w</var>
   <sub>1</sub>
   ·
   <var>y</var>
   <sub>1</sub>
   + 2 ·
   <var>w</var>
   <sub>2</sub>
   ·
   <var>y</var>
   <sub>2</sub>
   +
   <var>w</var>
   <sub>3</sub>
   ·
   <var>y</var>
   <sub>3</sub>
   = 2 · 0.115 · 0.308 + 2 · 0.483 · 0.738 + 0.785 · 1 = 1.57
  </span>
 </p>
 <p>
  Error -
  <span class="eq">
   <var>δ</var>
   <sub>DE</sub>
   =
   <span class="dvc">
    <b class="b0">|</b>
    <var>I</var>
    <sub>DE</sub>
    −
    <var>I</var>
    <b class="b0">|</b>
    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    <var>I</var>
   </span>
   =
   <span class="dvc">
    <b class="b0">|</b>
    1.57 − 1.57
    <b class="b0">|</b>
    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    1.57
   </span>
   = 0.0751
   <i>%</i>
  </span>
 </p>
